{"tid":2141123,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"幫兇之惡 - 李純恩","createTime":"2020-08-05T12:28:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T12:28:43.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e00d44a7c439e398f4fa9cecf12102d69cac8932","tid":2141123,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T12:28:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200805/4FKLUZTBT5AKDFWCYDDVLL7ECQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200805%2F4FKLUZTBT5AKDFWCYDDVLL7ECQ%2F&d=0%2B8fQjowpNY%2FdBz24eqX%2F5tjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=f26a3b22\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200805%2F4FKLUZTBT5AKDFWCYDDVLL7ECQ%2F&h=7e06a6dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200805/4FKLUZTBT5AKDFWCYDDVLL7ECQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n幫兇之惡 - 李純恩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/rqYQsIm7KB6sGSuSqXcfD3gaNCI=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/G3PTPIDE7RHU7G4JOGPRZYCADI.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FrqYQsIm7KB6sGSuSqXcfD3gaNCI%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FG3PTPIDE7RHU7G4JOGPRZYCADI.png&h=6ac228d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n互聯網<br />\n<br />\n前兩天寫了中國那本叫《平安經》的神經，原來故事還沒有完。<br />\n<br />\n寫這本神經的人叫賀電，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n雖然如此處理，。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n由此可見許多壞事，主謀可惡，幫兇更加可惡。如果沒有幫兇，主謀孤掌難鳴，能否成事都不知道，但只要有幫兇，壞事必成，並且變本加厲。就像這部《平安經》，如果沒有官媒和「專家」、「學者」這些幫兇們的推波助瀾，怎能借什麼「正能量助力」之名，差點變成又一部欺世盜名愚弄老百姓的「神經」？一本爛書如此，各類政治運動也一樣，比如「文革」，若只有「偉大領袖」策劃，而無「中央領導同志們」附和，全國的「革命群眾」和「知識份子」如癡如狂參與，又哪能變出一場「十年浩劫」！這就是幫兇的可惡之處。只是人們往往太專注於主謀而忽略了幫兇，給了他們一而再，再而三成為幫兇的機會。"}]}